The palace was a strong and imposing building,{{Cite adventurers league/A Wrinkle in the Weave|12}} the largest of all [[Shoonach]].{{Cite adventurers league/A Wrinkle in the Weave|5}}
It was made of stone and sported two levels: the first floor contained public rooms and entertaining chambers, whereas the second floor contained bedchambers used by the dignitaries and their guests.
The palace was surrounded by beautiful gardens that were bound by walls&mdash;something quite unusual for the region.
